text: Nedyalkov (Cyrillic: Недялков) is a Slavic masculine surname, its feminine counterpart is Nedyalkova. It may refer to *Anton Nedyalkov (born 1993), Bulgarian footballer *Georgi Nedyalkov (born 1989), Bulgarian footballer * Anjela Nedyalkova, (born 1991), Bulgarian actress Category:Bulgarian-language surnames
title: Nedyalkov
